title: Chinese space tourism startup eyes 2028 for 1st crewed mission, signs celebrity for future flight
description: InterstellOr is already taking bookings for its planned suborbital flights and says it has attracted its first celebrity passenger, highlighting China's growing commercial space ambitions.
